	(text "Filter out HF no resistors allowed\n\nCommon Mode Filtering (Inputs): To manage high \\(dV/dt\\) transients on the FET source pin (which is shared with the current sensing pin), a capacitor can be placed between the SNx and SPx pins.\nSmart Gate Drive Impact: The DRV8353 features Smart Gate Drive (SGD) technology, which regulates MOSFET gate current. Because the SPx pin is used as the low-side source reference for the gate driver, adding series resistors on the input pins can affect the gate drive performance."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 190.754 136.398 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "f2945910-7f3f-4466-a911-eae6d7530dfd")
	)
